{"tid":276423,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布熱狗成為香港政壇第一公害","createTime":"2017-06-08T20:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T07:50:19.000Z","uid":32051,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f222c50501e815b151db36f31177bdb9d8c92e92","tid":276423,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T20:28:23.000Z","msg":"大家都知建制土共爪牙，泛民關鍵賣港，自決只是新泛民。<br />\n<br />\n但佢地對香港嘅禍害都唔及熱狗嚟得深。<br />\n<br />\n熱狗由清算，清黨，再到近日被踢爆篤數陰私後，已經接二連三有意圖並有行動篤灰。<br />\n<br />\n熱狗今天做的，是要剷除最後熱愛香港、並有行動力的人。<br />\n先不討論發覺佬是否太戇鳩，俾人玩咁耐都唔走，定佢係舊登點柒，教車鍾意百屌學神也好。<br />\n我只著眼於熱狗的行為，是對一位鐵骨錚錚的漢子的私怨追殺。<br />\n<br />\n我先前也並非全取信發覺佬對熱狗的評語，但依幾日睇到熱狗所作所為。<br />\n<br />\n我幾肯定剔除發覺佬個人感情等問題，發覺佬對熱狗指控乃屬實情。<br />\n<br />\n試問如非篤到痛處，又何須百般報復。<br />\n<br />\n希望，仲對香港存有幻想的人，認清熱狗的真面目，不要再對其存有丁點希望。<br />\n<br />\n熱狗到底只是狗，專咬愛香港的人。"},{"pid":"644e34f43fb128cd55c2e42a96cdd42c4f2791b4","tid":276423,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30df6c6f9f21538f4dcd5bba8b0115fb420650df","tid":276423,"uid":14441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:05:37.000Z","msg":"Agger 垃圾黃洋達 關鍵時刻粒水 又成日叫人課金 自己又年年去旅行 又無正職 錢從何來 射撚滿又周圍溝女"},{"pid":"e543ec486fb07e14f16617e084fe0949f5e81697","tid":276423,"uid":105825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"熱血公民收皮"},{"pid":"72b673d534e529c140e7a458184601d6d58daa65","tid":276423,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"507ecc71840f365b9a78807591f15734dbc63cae","tid":276423,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"其實當發覺熱狗做野既同五毛一樣時，除左傻既，點會有人仲信熱狗<br />\n<br />\n日日用港豬左膠呢D空泛詞黎洗人腦<br />\n之後又做返佢地口中港豬左膠會做既野，根本就係龍門任佢擺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5252ca2f167e2073da472613c2ea6cd16f96421","tid":276423,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:58:25.000Z","msg":"第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一一定係城邦集團"},{"pid":"f50ff5ef7c6656e85fe673591ed46b24edbee9a2","tid":276423,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一一定係城邦集團</blockquote><br />\n人地熱城一家親，根本同一集團"},{"pid":"4a9241c383f4fae97ce2bce04eae6f0b7d08b893","tid":276423,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一一定係城邦集團</blockquote><br />\n人地熱城一家親，根本同一集團</blockquote><br />\n大難當前各自飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42fb884f8098a5807f90581b94eb326e1da01c6","tid":276423,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一一定係城邦集團</blockquote><br />\n人地熱城一家親，根本同一集團</blockquote><br />\n大難當前各自飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣云伯又話, 自己被迫支持<del><span style=\"color: red;\">毓民</span></del>熱狗"}]}